                    <p class="about-description">IndiaKart is a modern premium e-commerce platform delivering quality
                        products across India with speed, security, and a smile.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Mission -->
        <div class="mission-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="mission-grid">
                    <div class="mission-image">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556742049-0cfed4f6a45d?w=800&h=600&fit=crop"
                            alt="Our Mission">
                        <div class="image-overlay"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mission-content">
                        <span class="section-label">Our Mission</span>
                        <h2>Revolutionizing the Online Shopping Experience</h2>
                        <p>At IndiaKart, we're committed to providing a seamless shopping experience that combines
                            quality products, competitive prices, and exceptional customer service. Our mission is to
                            make premium products accessible to everyone across India.</p>
                        <ul class="mission-points">
                            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i><span>Quality products from trusted global
                                    brands</span></li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i><span>Fast and reliable delivery nationwide</span>
                            </li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i><span>Giving Quality Service</span>
                            </li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i><span>24/7 customer support for your queries</span>
                            </li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i><span>Keeping Your Trust</span>
                            </li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i><span>Secure payment and data protection</span></li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i><span>Easy 30-day hassle-free returns</span></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Values -->
        <div class="values-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:48px;">
                    <span class="section-label">Our Values</span>
                    <h2 class="section-title">What We Stand For</h2>
                    <p style="color:var(--text-mid);max-width:500px;margin:12px auto 0;">These core values guide
                        everything we do</p>
                </div>
                <div class="values-grid">
                    <div class="value-card">
                        <div class="value-icon"><i class="fas fa-heart"></i></div>
                        <h3>Customer First</h3>
                        <p>Your satisfaction is our top priority. We go above and beyond to ensure the best experience.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="value-card">
                        <div class="value-icon"><i class="fas fa-gem"></i></div>
                        <h3>Quality Promise</h3>
                        <p>We only offer premium products that meet our strict quality standards and exceed
                            expectations.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="value-card">
                        <div class="value-icon"><i class="fas fa-handshake"></i></div>
                        <h3>Integrity</h3>
                        <p>Honest pricing, transparent policies, and ethical business practices define our commitment.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="value-card">
                        <div class="value-icon"><i class="fas fa-rocket"></i></div>
                        <h3>Innovation</h3>
                        <p>We continuously improve our platform to provide the best technology and features.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Timeline -->
        <div class="timeline-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:16px;">
                    <span class="section-label">Our Journey</span>
                    <h2 class="section-title">Growing Together</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline">
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <div class="timeline-year">2024</div>
                            <h3>The Beginning</h3>
                            <p>IndiaKart was founded with a vision to transform online shopping in India, starting with
                                a curated selection of premium products.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <div class="timeline-year">2025</div>
                            <h3>Rapid Growth</h3>
                            <p>Expanded to 50+ cities with over 10,000 happy customers and 5,000+ products sold across
                                all categories.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <div class="timeline-year">2026</div>
                            <h3>New Heights</h3>
                            <p>Continuing to innovate and serve our growing community with premium products and enhanced
                                delivery experience.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
